'''Yuga Shrine''' or '''Yoga Shrine''' (由加神社 / 瑜伽神社, Yuga Jinja, Yūga Jinja)
* {{ill|Yuga Shrine Honmiya|ja|由加神社本宮}} - Located on Mount Yuga in [[Kojima, Kurashiki|Kojima]], [[Kurashiki City]], Okayama Prefecture. * Branch shrines of Yuga Shrine Honmiya. There are 52 branch shrines across Japan<ref>[http://www.yugasan.or.jp/massya-meguri/meguri01.html Yuga Shrine Pilgrimage] Yuga Shrine Honmiya</ref>. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Chūō-ku, Osaka)|ja|由加神社 (大阪市中央区)}} - Located in [[Chūō-ku, Osaka]], Osaka Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Nishinari-ku, Osaka)|ja|由加神社 (大阪市西成区)}} - Located in [[Nishinari-ku, Osaka]], Osaka Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Daijin|ja|由賀大神}} - Located in [[Abeno-ku, Osaka]], Osaka Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Taishi Town)|ja|由加神社 (太子町)}} - Located in [[Taishi, Hyōgo|Taishi Town]], [[Ibo District, Hyōgo|Ibo District]], Hyōgo Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Inari Shrine|ja|由加稲荷神社}} - Located in [[Himeji]], Hyōgo Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yoga Shrine (Nara City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (奈良市)}} - Located in [[Takahata-chō, Nara]], on the slopes of Mount Yoga, Nara Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Naka-ku, Okayama)|ja|由加神社 (岡山市中区)}} - Located in [[Naka-ku, Okayama]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Kita-ku, Okayama)|ja|由加神社 (岡山市北区)}} - Located in [[Kita-ku, Okayama]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Kurashiki)|ja|由加神社 (倉敷市)}} - Located in [[Mizushima, Kurashiki]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Wake Town)|ja|由加神社 (和気町)}} - Located in [[Wake, Okayama|Wake Town]], [[Wake District]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yoga Shrine (Tokushima City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (徳島市)}} - Located in [[Tokushima City]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yoga Daibosatsu|ja|瑜伽大菩薩}} - Located in Tokushima City, Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yoga Shrine (Komatsushima City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (小松島市)}} - Located in [[Komatsushima]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Iuga Shrine|ja|伊宇賀神社}} - Located in [[Naruto, Tokushima|Naruto City]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yoga Shrine (Yoshinogawa City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (吉野川市)}} - Located in [[Yoshinogawa]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Sakaide)|ja|由加神社 (坂出市)}} - Located in [[Sakaide]], Kagawa Prefecture. There are two shrines with the same name in the city. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Usa City)|ja|愈加神社}} - Located in [[Usa, Ōita|Usa City]], Ōita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of [[Usa Jingū]]. ** {{ill|Yoga Palace|ja|瑜伽宮}} - Located in [[Kunisaki, Ōita|Kunisaki City]], Oita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of the {{ill|Iwakura Shrine|ja|岩倉社}}. ** {{ill|Yoga Shrine (Usuki City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (臼杵市)}} - Located in [[Usuki, Ōita|Usuki City]], Ōita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of {{ill|Fukura Tenmangū|ja|福良天満宮}}.
