d}} - Located in [[:en:Naka-ku, Okayama|Naka-ku, Okayama]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Kita-ku, Okayama)|ja|由加神社 (岡山市北区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Kita-ku, Okayama)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Kita-ku, Okayama|Kita-ku, Okayama]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Kurashiki)|ja|由加神社 (倉敷市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Kurashiki)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[Mizushima, Kurashiki]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Wake Town)|ja|由加神社 (和気町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Wake Town)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Wake, Okayama|Wake Town]], [[Wake District]], Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Tokushima City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (徳島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Tokushima City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Tokushima City|Tokushima City]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Daibosatsu|ja|瑜伽大菩薩|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Daibosatsu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Tokushima City, Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Komatsushima City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (小松島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Komatsushima City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Komatsushima|Komatsushima]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Iuga Shrine|ja|伊宇賀神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iuga Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Naruto, Tokushima|Naruto City]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Yoshinogawa City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (吉野川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Yoshinogawa City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Yoshinogawa|Yoshinogawa]], Tokushima Prefecture. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Sakaide)|ja|由加神社 (坂出市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Sakaide)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Sakaide|Sakaide]], Kagawa Prefecture. There are two shrines with the same name in the city. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Usa City)|ja|愈加神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Usa City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Usa, Ōita|Usa City]], Ōita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of [[Usa Jingū]]. ** {{ill|Yuga Palace|ja|瑜伽宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Palace|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Kunisaki, Ōita|Kunisaki City]], Oita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of the {{ill|Iwakura Shrine|ja|岩倉社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakura Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. ** {{ill|Yuga Shrine (Usuki City)|ja|瑜伽神社 (臼杵市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Shrine (Usuki City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Usuki, Ōita|Usuki City]], Ōita Prefecture, as a subordinate shrine of {{ill|Fukura Tenmangū|ja|福良天満宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukura Tenmangū|qq=}}.
